title: Account has been reset?
body:
I logged on to League today with my account details as per usual, when I logged in it asked me for my summoner name ( at this time I assumed it was a bug of some sort) anyway I logged into it and put my usual name "ArchieTheLeftNut" when I pressed continue/enter {what ever it was} it took me to the home screen and I was level 1. I immediately checked my match history and there was nothing there on the client, also all of my champions/skins were gone. So I came on this site and checked my match history of my Character and my games from last night are still there but when I search up my name on the client it just shows me the level 1 profile. Any help/fixes would be deeply appreciated, I have spent easily $600+ on this game and i'mquite worried/angry. Hard getting money as a student.

Thanks in advance!

replies.body:
Hey there,

From what I can tell you have a level 1 account on NA, it's possible you logged into this account by mistake.

Please open your launcher and make sure your client is set to OCE.
